Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait' activities before transitioning to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Minimum duration from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total duration for 'Accepted + Wait' activities within cases that involve 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Minimum duration for 'Accepted + Wait' to be followed by 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Average duration it takes from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total duration it takes 'Accepted + Wait' to transition to any subsequent activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + Wait' in cases leading to 'Completed + In Call' versus cases leading to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Average duration for 'Accepted + Wait' in cases with 'High' impact versus 'Medium' or 'Low' impact
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Total resolution time of cases starting with 'Accepted + Wait' and ending with 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Minimum duration between 'Accepted + Wait' and the next occurrence of 'Accepted + Wait'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Elapsed time between 'Accepted + Wait' and 'Completed + Closed' in the same case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Time from 'Accepted + Wait' to 'Completed + In Call' in cases with multiple occurrences of 'Accepted + Wait'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: 'Accepted + Wait' Cycle Time in cases with 'Completed + In Call' as the final activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + In Call'
